{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.000", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.320", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.960", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren auf den Besucherr\u00e4ngen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.120", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dem Antrag der Fraktion Die Linke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.560", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Mindestlohn auf 12\u00a0Euro zu erh\u00f6hen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir hier keinen neuen Antrag vorliegen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.400", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vielleicht in dieser Legislaturperiode, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.520", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber ansonsten ist der Antrag bekannt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.280", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Grunds\u00e4tzlich war es hier in Deutschland immer gute Praxis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.000", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Lohnfindung Aufgabe der Tarifpartner ist bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.800", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Parteien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.600", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Arbeitsvertrag stehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.360", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hat sich in der Vergangenheit bew\u00e4hrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.720", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie unsere wirtschaftliche Situation zeigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.840", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und daran sollten wir auch festhalten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dem Mindestlohngesetz hat der Gesetzgeber in der letzten Legislaturperiode erstmals eine Ausnahme von diesem Grundsatz gemacht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.360", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei sollte es aber bleiben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.680", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Intention damals war, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.960", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.840", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir setzen den Mindestlohn auf eine Untergrenze von 8,50\u00a0Euro fest."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.920", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danach sollte aber\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.400", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so war die Vereinbarung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.200", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Gesetzgeber nicht mehr t\u00e4tig werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.040", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um eine Politisierung des Mindestlohns zu verhindern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.520", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Anpassung sollte in der Verantwortung der Mindestlohnkommission liegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.400", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil diese parit\u00e4tisch mit den Tarifpartnern besetzt ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Verankerung ist auch richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.840", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.840", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei der Lohnanpassung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.320", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die alle zwei Jahre stattfindet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.840", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat die Mindestlohnkommission genaue Ma\u00dfst\u00e4be anzulegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.560", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie hat die gesamte Situation und alle Einfl\u00fcsse auf die Lohnfindung vollumf\u00e4nglich zu ber\u00fccksichtigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.880", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie hat also die gesamtwirtschaftliche Situation unseres Landes zu ber\u00fccksichtigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.360", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Mindestlohnkommission ist im Jahre\u00a02016 schon t\u00e4tig geworden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.960", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem sie den Mindestlohn auf 8,84\u00a0Euro erh\u00f6ht hat\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.400", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sie wird sich im kommenden Sommer wieder turnusm\u00e4\u00dfig mit der H\u00f6he des Mindestlohns besch\u00e4ftigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.800", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was Sie mit Ihrem Antrag wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.440", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.200", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Grundregeln des Mindestlohngesetzes au\u00dfer Kraft zu setzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.480", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen n\u00e4mlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.480", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Lohnfindung nicht mehr bei den Tarifpartnern liegt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.880", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen quasi eine Planwirtschaft einf\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.600", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das lehnen wir nat\u00fcrlich strikt ab. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.720", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sollten Sie mit Blick auf die Geschichte unseres Landes auch wissen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.840", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man \u00c4nderungen am Mindestlohngesetz vornehmen will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann sollte man eher den Weg w\u00e4hlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.080", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es rechtssicherer und unb\u00fcrokratischer zu machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.200", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich nenne zum Beispiel das Stichwort \u201eGeneralunternehmerhaftung\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.400", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das in der heutigen Debatte noch nicht gefallen ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.320", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist f\u00fcr einen Unternehmer nicht so einfach, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.640", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der n\u00e4chsten Stufe selber nachzuweisen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.840", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass er Sorgfalt ausge\u00fcbt hat und ihm nichts vorzuwerfen ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.240", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Dokumentationspflichten sind bereits angesprochen worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.440", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich brauchen wir eine Dokumentation der L\u00f6hne und Arbeitszeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.960", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Fehlverhalten und Fehlhandlungen feststellen und sie anschlie\u00dfend auch ahnden zu k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allerdings muss man dann die Frage stellen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.840", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "An welcher Stelle fangen wir mit den Dokumentationen an? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.200", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir festlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass noch bei einer Lohnh\u00f6he von 2\u00a0958\u00a0Euro\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.720", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist mehr als das Doppelte des Mindestlohns\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.760", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dokumentationen erfolgen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.320", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann halte ich diesen Betrag f\u00fcr zu hoch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.680", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er sollte meines Erachtens gesenkt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.600", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die eigentliche Kerngrenze, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.560", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an der es prek\u00e4r werden kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.880", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weitaus niedriger liegt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.320", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass die Arbeitgeber bei dem hohen Betrag noch entsprechende Dokumentationen vornehmen sollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.600", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist meiner Auffassung nach nicht verh\u00e4ltnism\u00e4\u00dfig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.880", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein weiterer Punkt ist meines Erachtens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.280", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie man mit Verst\u00f6\u00dfen und Sanktionen umgeht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.360", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich muss ein Versto\u00df gegen das Mindestlohngesetz sanktioniert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.600", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das steht schon wegen der Wettbewerbsfreiheit au\u00dfer Frage. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.640", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber einen Ausschluss von \u00f6ffentlichen Vergabeverfahren bereits bei einer Bu\u00dfgeldh\u00f6he von 2\u00a0500\u00a0Euro\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.080", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei einer maximalen Bu\u00dfgeldh\u00f6he von 500\u00a0000\u00a0Euro\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.520", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also bei 0,5\u00a0Prozent der maximalen Bu\u00dfgeldh\u00f6he, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.160", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "halte ich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.760", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ehrlich gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.160", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr unverh\u00e4ltnism\u00e4\u00dfig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.960", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das w\u00e4ren Punkte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.480", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denen man sich widmen sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.440", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "statt den Antr\u00e4gen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.960", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie stellen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.600", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.120", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.760", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wilfried Oellers.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.480", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chste Rednerin: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.000", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kerstin Griese f\u00fcr die SPD-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}